1
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:02,560
This is it.

2
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,160
Turn on the recorder.

3
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:06,440
Are you sure?

4
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,160
Absolutely.

5
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:09,320
In the middle of the night,

6
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,440
I was passing by here

7
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:12,760
and saw Huang Hankun peeing here.

8
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:14,400
It scared the hell out of me.

9
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:16,039
I thought I saw a ghost.

10
00:01:16,039 --> 00:01:17,160
When you were carrying the body,

11
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:18,400
did you see his face?

12
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:20,760
Do you think it was Huang Hankun?

13
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,240
I didn't dare to look either.

14
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:25,039
When we were carrying the body,

15
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:27,240
Wang Yu covered Huang Hankun with a blanket.

16
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,280
He said the dead

17
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:29,720
aren't presentable.

18
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:30,600
Take him away quickly.

19
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:31,530
Okay, Director.

20
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:32,120
Come on.

21
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,520
Easy.

22
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:40,920
Was Huang Hankun fat or thin?

23
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:41,920
Quite thin.

24
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:44,360
Then when you carried the body,

25
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,560
didn't it feel heavy?

26
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:48,720
Don't dead people get all bloated?

27
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:51,120
I didn't pay much attention at the time.

28
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:51,960
Buddy,

29
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,090
Huang Hankun

30
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:55,289
isn't actually still alive, is he?

31
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:02,200
The time of death was 10:30 PM.

32
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,160
According to Wang Yu's description,

33
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:06,320
the victim was fixing a light

34
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:07,440
when he was electrocuted,

35
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:09,960
and his head hit the transformer on the ground.

36
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,720
But the transformer the police confiscated

37
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:13,640
tested positive for pig blood.

38
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:14,440
Also,

39
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,920
my autopsy results show

40
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:17,920
that his head

41
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,720
was injured by the back of an axe,

42
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:22,400
which doesn't match the transformer at all.

43
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,260
In other words,

44
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:25,140
Wang Yu gave false testimony.

45
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:27,400
Why would Wang Yu give false testimony?

46
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,440
Does that mean

47
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:30,930
it's very likely

48
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,610
they committed murder?

49
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:36,360
Then where did her husband, Huang Hankun, go?

50
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,840
That means the two of them committed the murder together.

51
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:41,320
They staged the scene together

52
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,720
and disguised the body.

53
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:44,320
But that was six hours later,

54
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,840
around 4:30 AM.

55
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:48,040
Rigor mortis had already set in by then.

56
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:48,600
So,

57
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,810
when they were shaving him,

58
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:53,370
that's why they left scrape marks on his face.

59
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,520
They've watched too many dramas about swapping identities.

60
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,120
Let's go.

61
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:12,440
The toothbrush from Li Jun's home was tested,

62
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:15,040
and it matches the DNA of the body in the coffin.

63
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,880
It is Li Jun.

64
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:18,120
Every household in the village has a motorbike.

65
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:20,560
Plus, many people came back for the holiday.

66
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:21,600
One extra bike

67
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,200
would go unnoticed.

68
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:25,840
Bali Village isn't far from here, is it?

69
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,120
Has Li Jun been here before?

70
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,480
Li Jun

71
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,640
is from the neighboring village.

72
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:30,900
We don't know him well.

73
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:33,400
Huang Hankun from our village

74
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:34,770
isn't very popular.

75
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,720
A few years ago,

76
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,280
creditors often came

77
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,280
to collect debts.

78
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,000
Ever since

79
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,560
his daughter passed away,

80
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,680
the debt collectors

81
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,760
stopped coming.

82
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:45,400
Who is Huang Hankun's wife, Wang Yu,

83
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,840
close to?

84
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,329
She's quite close with my wife.

85
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,600
She doesn't interact much with others.

86
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,640
Since she came to the village,

87
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,640
I haven't seen her family visit.

88
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,000
Even when her child

89
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,200
passed away,

90
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:00,200
none of her family

91
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,440
showed up.

92
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:04,050
What exactly happened to their child?

93
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,240
That little girl

94
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,400
only started primary school last year.

95
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,860
On the first day of school,

96
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:12,200
when Huang Hankun took her to school.

97
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,860
Hurry up. You're going to be late for school.

98
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,970
Come and pick me up early after school.

99
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,320
Go to school now.

100
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,320
Study hard.

101
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,360
Don't be late.

102
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:35,960
Take this.

103
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,200
Read for a bit.

104
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,000
Mhm.

105
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:05,840
Dad.

106
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:07,520
Dad.

107
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:08,960
Dad.

108
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,200
I'll look for him for you.

109
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,000
Panpan.

110
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:52,880
Panpan.

111
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,440
Panpan.

112
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:56,800
Panpan.

113
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:59,360
For this child to be born into such a family,

114
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,640
it's really quite pitiful.

115
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:02,800
It was only after the incident

116
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,480
that we found out

117
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,210
about Huang Hankun's drug use.

118
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,200
Wang Yu didn't dare

119
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:08,240
tell the villagers anything either.

120
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,570
After the child's grandparents arrived,

121
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:12,560
they cried and cursed a bit.

122
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,680
The news about the drug use

123
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:15,880
just started spreading in the village.

124
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,690
The forensic report is out.

125
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,980
The person in the coffin is Li Jun.

126
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:26,690
Huang Hankun and Wang Yu are both missing now.

127
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,290
Their phones are unreachable too.

128
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,280
The surveillance at the village entrance

129
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:31,880
didn't capture them either.

130
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:34,000
These two have no phones,

131
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,800
and transportation is inconvenient.

132
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,960
Plus, right now,

133
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:39,520
they definitely wouldn't dare use their ID cards.

134
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,480
They probably didn't get far.

135
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,340
Could they have run off together?

136
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,340
It's possible.

137
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:45,650
They left in a hurry.

138
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,000
At Wang Yu's home,

139
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,760
there was no obvious vehicle.

140
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:50,960
So they most likely went on foot.

141
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,320
Wang Yu did lie to us.

142
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:55,080
So there is another possibility.

143
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:57,280
If Huang Hankun killed Li Jun,

144
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,840
it at least proves

145
00:06:58,840 --> 00:06:59,720
that she knows the truth.

146
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,120
Given Huang Hankun's personality,

147
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,680
to someone who knows the truth,

148
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,280
it's hard to say what he'd do.

149
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,080
So,

150
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:07,120
Wang Yu might have left on her own,

151
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,040
or she might have been forced.

152
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:10,080
I learned during my visit to the village

153
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:12,140
that Huang Hankun often beat Wang Yu.

154
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:14,200
So it's possible Wang Yu was coerced.

155
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:16,880
After how Huang Hankun treated Wang Yu,

156
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,880
do you think she'd run away with him?

157
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:20,680
If they didn't run off together,

158
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,260
where would Wang Yu go?

159
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,320
As for the nearby villages,

160
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:25,250
we've sent police to investigate.

161
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:28,320
They'll let us know as soon as there are results.

162
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:28,680
Alright.

163
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,880
Let's not sit around.

164
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,060
Let's go to Wang Yu's parents' house.

165
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:44,080
Look at how we're living now.

166
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,480
What kind of life is this?

167
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,640
At least we had a home before.

168
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:50,720
But look at us now.

169
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,720
It's a good thing I met your parents.

170
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:02,280
They're the only ones who have ever been good to me.

171
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,900
My mom is half-paralyzed.

172
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,320
She needs constant care.

173
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:21,120
I have to carry her to the toilet now.

174
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,400
What about your two sisters?

175
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,680
Do they come back often?

176
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,760
My eldest sister

177
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:26,000
during the New Year,

178
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,860
came back once.

179
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,120
My second sister.

180
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,320
She never comes back.

181
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:31,280
What's the point of raising daughters?

182
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,210
They get married

183
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,159
or move away.

184
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:35,799
I still have to rely on my son.

185
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:38,039
If you'd treated Eldest Sister and Second Sister better,

186
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,200
you could have counted on them.

187
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,799
I want to go work out of town, too.

188
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,400
But with the state you're in,

189
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:43,880
how can I leave?

190
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,640
What year did Wang Yu leave?

191
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:46,520
I think...

192
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:47,640
2005.

193
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:48,840
2005.

194
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,720
She hasn't been back for thirteen years.

195
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,380
Does she usually contact you?

196
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,730
She must really hate us.

197
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:58,720
Second Sister.

198
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,450
Why aren't you eating the corn?

199
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:01,720
What are you doing?

200
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,320
I said I'm not eating it.

201
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:05,040
Your brother meant well.

202
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,920
Why are you yelling at him?

203
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,160
He burned me.

204
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:09,780
You complain even a drop of cold water burns.

205
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:28,800
Your hands are hurt.

206
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:30,320
Why are you still touching cold water?

207
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,650
You'll get chilblains.

208
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,600
Let me wash it for you.

209
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:49,640
I broke it again.

210
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,840
She's going to scold me again.

211
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:56,180
I really don't want to stay here anymore.

212
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,320
It's okay.

213
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:01,920
You...

214
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,680
just say I broke it.

215
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:05,360
Then you'll be fine.

216
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,680
Dry your hands first.

217
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,880
Not cold anymore, right?

218
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,900
Let me show you something.

219
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:26,560
This...

220
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,120
is from the city.

221
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,520
Smell it.

222
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,140
Does it smell good?

223
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,610
Smells good, right?

224
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:43,740
It's all our fault.

225
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:46,080
We let my sister down.

226
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,440
What is there to be sorry for?

227
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:50,240
Like a greedy cat with a bone,

228
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:52,050
she couldn't wait a single day.

229
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,720
I never said I wouldn't let her marry.

230
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:56,320
She just had to run off with that red-haired punk.

231
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,520
Huangjiazhuang is quite far from here.

232
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,760
How did they meet?

233
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:02,640
Huang Hankun's grandfather is from our village.

234
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:04,760
When he came here for New Year's,

235
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:06,090
he met my second sister.

236
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,440
They got together.

237
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:09,040
His family was better off

238
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:10,280
than ours.

239
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,600
So Mom wanted to ask

240
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,000
for a higher bride price.

241
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,860
But he couldn't afford that much.

242
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:16,240
So Mom wouldn't

243
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:18,920
let Second Sister be with him.

244
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:21,450
But your sister was only sixteen then.

245
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:24,360
Sixteen is practically a grown woman.

246
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:27,040
If a good family wants her,

247
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,040
as her mother,

248
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:29,100
how could I refuse?

249
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,280
You asked for so much back then.

250
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,400
He didn't even want to be with my sister anymore.

251
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:34,040
In the end,

252
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:36,200
didn't she run off with that man anyway?

253
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:38,120
That man didn't pay a single cent.

254
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,840
If your second sister hadn't left back then,

255
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,770
I'll find her another good family.

256
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:44,920
I want at least a cow, no matter what.

257
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:48,480
I'm doing all this for you.

258
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:55,060
So, how are things with her

259
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,170
and that guy now?

260
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,400
They're still together.

261
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,330
They had a child.

262
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:00,720
A boy or a girl?

263
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,040
A girl.

264
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:04,640
She died in a car accident.

265
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:05,560
Oh.

266
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:11,080
I don't think Huang Hankun and Wang Yu

267
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,320
will come back here.

268
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,880
I think so too.

269
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:15,970
Let's head back to the station.

270
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,800
I didn't expect a swim would turn into this.

271
00:12:56,800 --> 00:12:58,000
It scared me to death.

272
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:57,280
The victim has multiple stab wounds on the back.

273
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,640
The body is severely decomposed.

274
00:13:58,640 --> 00:13:59,640
It exhibits bloating,

275
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,920
and there is a lot of mucus on the skin surface.

276
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:02,920
And his hands,

277
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:09,840
the skin is sloughing off like gloves.

278
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:10,700
Captain Zheng,

279
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:13,280
ask Chen Yishi and Sun Quan to help me turn him over.

280
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:13,760
Okay.

281
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:20,920
Dr. Dai,

282
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,460
what should I do with this?

283
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,040
Take it to get prints.

284
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:32,280
The eyes are completely clouded.

285
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,360
The body has developed

286
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:34,720
marbling and blisters.

287
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:38,240
Preliminary time of death is over 48 hours.

288
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:41,600
Also,

289
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:44,680
this person likely had a history of drug abuse.

290
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:46,860
For the detailed autopsy,

291
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,540
help me take the body back.

292
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:54,320
Judging by the victim's physical features,

293
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,000
he is very likely

294
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:57,400
Huang Hankun, whom we've been looking for.

295
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:57,840
Sun Quan,

296
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:58,800
assist Dai Yu.

297
00:14:58,920 --> 00:15:00,240
Confirm the identity of the deceased immediately.

298
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:00,880
Gao Zhuang.

299
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:01,360
Jin Jin.

300
00:15:01,520 --> 00:15:02,180
Chen Yishi.

301
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,920
Our top priority right now

302
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:05,160
is to find Wang Yu.

303
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:14,920
Hello.

304
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:17,240
Hello.

305
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,680
Have you seen this woman?

306
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,000
No, I haven't.

307
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:22,680
Thank you.

308
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:25,800
Sir.

309
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:26,760
Sir.

310
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,780
Have you seen this person?

311
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:30,600
No.

312
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:31,600
Excuse me.

313
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:33,060
Have you seen this person?

314
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:34,240
No.

315
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:35,720
No.

316
00:15:36,680 --> 00:15:38,680
Forensic Doctor Chu Mitang called.

317
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:41,480
The identity of the body in the water is confirmed.

318
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:42,540
It's Huang Hankun.

319
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,560
Huang Hankun's time of death was

320
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:47,080
the day we went to Huangjiazhuang for the exhumation.

321
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,540
We previously speculated

322
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,120
that in the Li Jun case, Wang Yu

323
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,080
was a witness,

324
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:52,680
and Huang Hankun was the mastermind.

325
00:15:52,680 --> 00:15:54,340
Now that Huang Hankun is dead,

326
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:56,680
Wang Yu's role is even harder to define.

327
00:15:57,280 --> 00:15:59,200
She likely went from being an accomplice

328
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,330
to being the killer.

329
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:03,300
So, what was the couple's motive for killing Li Jun?

330
00:16:03,680 --> 00:16:04,440
Money?

331
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:06,000
That doesn't make sense.

332
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:08,720
We've learned that Huang Hankun didn't owe Li Jun much money.

333
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:09,720
A crime of passion

334
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,400
doesn't make sense either.

335
00:16:11,400 --> 00:16:13,200
The relationship between their families isn't that complicated.

336
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:15,400
The key is that Wang Yu took such a big risk

337
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:17,600
to cover up the truth using Huang Hankun's death.

338
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,200
There's only one possibility left.

339
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,260
Impulsive murder.

340
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:22,480
In Huangjiazhuang,

341
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:23,160
Wang Yu's parents' home,

342
00:16:23,160 --> 00:16:23,720
and

343
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:24,880
her current residence,

344
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:26,320
we've arranged stakeouts.

345
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,680
But we haven't found any trace of her.

346
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:28,480
Also,

347
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:30,240
at Huang Hankun's parents' home,

348
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,680
we didn't get any useful information.

349
00:16:31,680 --> 00:16:32,280
Tell me,

350
00:16:32,560 --> 00:16:34,220
where could Wang Yu have gone?

351
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:35,120
On the roads leaving the city,

352
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:36,580
we've set up checkpoints.

353
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:38,000
She doesn't have a phone.

354
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,600
She shouldn't have gone far.

355
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:42,930
Your analysis makes sense.

356
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:44,450
Let me share my view.

357
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,920
Let's start with Huang Hankun's body.

358
00:16:47,920 --> 00:16:49,120
It was found

359
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,120
by the Ba River.

360
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,250
Based on the current

361
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:52,800
and the motor on the body,

362
00:16:52,800 --> 00:16:53,730
we can infer that

363
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:54,730
the dumping site

364
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:56,170
shouldn't be too far

365
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:58,040
from where the body was found.

366
00:16:58,720 --> 00:17:00,520
Within a one-kilometer radius.

367
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,240
Let's get back to Wang Yu.

368
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:04,369
Assuming she is the killer,

369
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:06,930
could she have disposed of the body alone?

370
00:17:07,319 --> 00:17:08,250
I don't think so.

371
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:10,599
Let's leave aside the transportation.

372
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:12,160
From her home to the Ba River,

373
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,440
it's about 20 kilometers.

374
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:15,079
She'd have to carry not only the body,

375
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:17,680
but also a motor weighing about 30 kilograms.

376
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:20,839
Obviously, a frail woman couldn't do that.

377
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:21,920
So, at the scene,

378
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:24,040
was there a second accomplice or killer?

379
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:25,400
We don't know any of this yet.

380
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,440
So finding Wang Yu

381
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,640
is our top priority.

382
00:17:29,080 --> 00:17:31,080
Huang Hankun is a long-term drug user.

383
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:32,280
Could it be one of his

384
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:33,800
fellow drug users?

385
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:36,200
All your speculations are possible.

386
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:36,800
Jinjin,

387
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:38,120
you're a woman.

388
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:41,320
You should understand women particularly well.

389
00:17:41,320 --> 00:17:42,840
If you were Wang Yu,

390
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:44,120
where would you go?

391
00:17:44,120 --> 00:17:46,520
We went to Wang Yu's parents' home earlier.

392
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:48,440
Her mother strongly favors sons over daughters

393
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:50,240
and has no affection for Wang Yu.

394
00:17:50,280 --> 00:17:51,000
So I feel

395
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:53,000
Wang Yu probably wouldn't go back there.

396
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:53,760
On the contrary,

397
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:55,200
according to what we know,

398
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,840
Wang Yu's in-laws

399
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:59,120
love her like their own daughter.

400
00:17:59,240 --> 00:17:59,760
The ones Wang Yu

401
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:00,960
is most worried about

402
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:02,240
should be her in-laws.

403
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:03,920
Their home?

404
00:18:04,120 --> 00:18:04,960
We just went there.

405
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:05,760
Just because she wasn't there before,

406
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:07,890
doesn't mean she didn't go back later.

407
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:08,450
Let's go.

408
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:12,680
Eat more.

409
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:15,240
Child.

410
00:18:15,800 --> 00:18:17,330
It's rare for you to come by.

411
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:19,450
Whether the food is good or not,

412
00:18:19,800 --> 00:18:20,480
