413
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:22,400
Look at you running around all day.

414
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,720
You've gotten so thin.

415
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:24,280
Yeah.

416
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:25,480
Thanks, Dad.

417
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:26,400
Thanks, Mom.

418
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:27,480
Let's eat.

419
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:30,480
Why did you bring all your melon seeds here?

420
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:32,680
You should have kept some for yourself.

421
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:34,400
Dad,

422
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:37,200
I want to do some other business.

423
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:40,200
It's a waste to leave the melon seeds sitting there.

424
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,800
You and Mom should sell them.

425
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:44,440
That works.

426
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:45,560
Yu'er,

427
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:48,200
did something happen?

428
00:18:48,480 --> 00:18:50,540
The police came by a couple of days ago

429
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,600
asking about you and Kunzi.

430
00:18:54,080 --> 00:18:54,760
The police?

431
00:18:55,080 --> 00:18:56,080
What did they say?

432
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:58,240
They just asked

433
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,570
if you two had come back.

434
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,280
They said

435
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,880
if you came back,

436
00:19:02,120 --> 00:19:04,000
we should give them a call.

437
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:05,840
I saw you come back yesterday,

438
00:19:05,840 --> 00:19:07,240
and you were in a bad mood,

439
00:19:07,520 --> 00:19:09,080
so I didn't bring it up.

440
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:10,240
I was afraid

441
00:19:10,560 --> 00:19:11,200
Kunzi

442
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:12,850
got in trouble again

443
00:19:13,320 --> 00:19:14,650
and it would affect you.

444
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:16,640
So I didn't tell the police.

445
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:21,280
It's okay, Mom.

446
00:19:21,720 --> 00:19:23,440
It's always the same stuff with Kunzi.

447
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:24,280
I'm used to it.

448
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:26,800
He's a piece of trash.

449
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:28,880
It might be better if he gets locked up.

450
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:29,440
Then we can

451
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:30,900
have some peace and quiet.

452
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:32,360
Don't say that.

453
00:19:32,920 --> 00:19:33,720
Dad.

454
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:34,840
Let's eat.
